CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `goalTemplateUsage` (
  `id` int AUTO_INCREMENT NOT NULL,
  `templateId` int NOT NULL,
  `employeeId` int NOT NULL,
  `pdiPlanId` int,
  `wasCustomized` boolean NOT NULL DEFAULT false,
  `customizations` json,
  `completed` boolean NOT NULL DEFAULT false,
  `completedAt` datetime,
  `successfullyCompleted` boolean NOT NULL DEFAULT false,
  `usedAt` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  CONSTRAINT `goalTemplateUsage_id` PRIMARY KEY(`id`)
);
